data.description:
Step into a world of enchantment at Living Sculpture Sanctuary, a hidden oasis nestled in the heart of Davie, Florida. Co-founded by Mary Luz Rodriguez Alvarez and Robert J. McKee, the Sanctuary is a living testament to their dedication to environmental stewardship, holistic wellness, and social justice, reflected in every corner of this unique haven. 

Immerse yourself in the Sanctuary's surroundings, where ancient oak trees whisper tales of old, serene waterfalls cascade rhythmically, and captivating bonsai displays tell a story of patience and care. The Sanctuary, a sought-after venue for weddings, life celebrations, and corporate events, weaves an atmosphere of tranquility and joy, creating memories that echo long after the moment has passed. 

At the heart of the Sanctuary lies a thriving Bonsai Center and plant nursery, a testament to our commitment to nature's splendor. Our dedicated breeding efforts have birthed an extraordinary array of Desert Roses, their vibrant, non-fading colors a spectacle exclusive to our center. 

Beyond these, we offer a unique space to celebrate and host a variety of events including weddings, corporate events, birthdays, celebrations of life, baby showers, etc. We believe that your day here should be one of the best days of your lives, and we strive to make it happen.
